title: MAcDuvall
author: MAcDuvall
content: I tried to withdraw followed the instructions paid for instant.  they sent a link to follow to check on transaction, says page not found.  My withdraw address shows no transaction and no money in my wallet.  It’s been well over 24 hours wtf

comments.author: jackg
comments.body: You might want to leave a post on their thread instead of here as they'll be more likely to see it: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=320959.0You could also send a message to TheQuin who used to work with them and probably still does: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?action=profile;u=143168 (if you send them something identifiable like you're uid then they can probably see and resolve the issue faster).

comments.author: Killredillla
comments.body: Quote from: MAcDuvall on May 13, 2022, 11:22:35 AMI tried to withdraw followed the instructions paid for instant.  they sent a link to follow to check on transaction, says page not found.  My withdraw address shows no transaction and no money in my wallet.  It’s been well over 24 hours wtfSometimes your transaction doesn't get broadcasted directly to the network and instead they take it for manual verification which can take up to 48h last time i checked.so i think this may be your case here.Any updates.. ?
